tip_battle.title: Dark Odin
tip_battle.message: The element of the first attack you use becomes effective against Dark Odin, but this awakens elemental power in him, too. To find a path to victory, think back on your previous battles with other creatures. Note that if you don't use an elemental attack, you'll be denied the chance to fight, and sent to the far reaches of the dimension. The final blow that Dark Odin unleashes can rend the very fabric of this Battle Record. Your chance of victory is slim if all his powers are awakened, so end the battle as quickly as you can. May fate be on your side...
